{"tid":1645224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位，發夢巴冇事 放心","createTime":"2019-10-10T21:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T07:29:22.000Z","uid":241868,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"cd9c9cf66036d30429d493d651a75e644bd1dda5","tid":1645224,"uid":241868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:20:00.000Z","msg":"我係發夢巴不自殺聲明入面 2個既其中一個<br />\n大家唔洗擔心 佢唔會有事 我都唔會比佢有事 會一直同佢keep contact<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GF4m9Nh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGF4m9Nh.png&h=1ce8b3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">然後請大家唔好相信 個個唯一神 講既任何野plz</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLCv29a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLCv29a.jpg&h=da379279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4MAuPg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4MAuPg.png&h=e074215a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">發夢巴唔會去做大家樂廚，因為佢只會煮野比我食</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98031a769dcc42f6efb8cd41b7f2bdb4b451fc9e","tid":1645224,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:20:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac58cc576a75a3198bb36cad610f6369002fd3e5","tid":1645224,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:21:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3acde02cd7b5d370c6fdab940f9c959624351792","tid":1645224,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:21:38.000Z","msg":"多謝報平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要生存到贏嗰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020b134fae678363cf415ddb1c1c